      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>*이 글은 생활코딩 WEB2 Node.js를 기반으로 쓰여진 글입니다.<br><a href="https://opentutorials.org/course/3332">생활코딩 Node.js</a></p><h3 id="소스코드"><a href="#소스코드" class="headerlink" title="소스코드"></a>소스코드</h3><p>readdir.js</p><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">var</span> testFolder = <span class="string">'./data'</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">var</span> fs = <span class="built_in">require</span>(<span class="string">'fs'</span>);</span><br><span class="line"> </span><br><span class="line">fs.readdir(testFolder, <span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span>(<span class="params">error, filelist</span>)</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="built_in">console</span>.log(filelist);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/image/nodejs_003-1.PNG" alt=""></p><p>readdir.js 를 실행시키면<br>data 폴더안에 있는 파일들의 이름들이 배열에 담겨서 출력되게 된다.</p><p><img src="/image/nodejs_003.PNG" alt=""></p>]]></content:encoded>
      
